My minimum hit went from 1 to 18.<br>
My maximum hit went from 587 to 735.<br>
My average hit went from 129 to 198.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
No offense but your smoking some good stuff there.<br>
<br>
minimum hit is affected by weapon delay and character level only.<br>
Maximum hit is affected by strength, weapon damage and delay and character level only.<br>
Average hit is determined by ATK.<br>
<br>
Punishing blade does nothing more than add an extra swing to 2h attacks on some rounds.  It does not affect how hard you hit, it does not affect how often you hit,  it does not affect minimum or maximum hits for any weapon in any way.<br>
<br>
Anyway with 1800 ATK, full offensive AA minus double riposte and ambidex, using a Twisted steel bastard sword I average 110-120 on level 60+ blues in the elemental planes.  I do slightly less with sparkling shortsword/primal combo. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#FF0000>- </font><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior>The Steel Warrior</a><font color=#FF0000> - </font><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena>The Arena</a> <font color=#FF0000> - </font><a href="http://www.steelwarrior.org">The Steel Warrior website</a><font color=#FF0000> - </font><br><br><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard®</a> Ver. 7.240<br>Copyright ©1999-2003 ezboard, Inc.</center></body></html>  

